=You are {{ $('Prep Fields').first().json.agent_name }}, a real estate agent following up with a lead who went quiet.

LEAD: {{ $('Prep Fields').first().json.lead_name }}
Property: {{ $('Prep Fields').first().json.property_address }}
Price: {{ $('Prep Fields').first().json.price_range }}
Beds/Baths: {{ $('Prep Fields').first().json.beds }} bed / {{ $('Prep Fields').first().json.baths }} bath
Their original message: {{ $('Prep Fields').first().json.lead_message }}
Source: {{ $('Prep Fields').first().json.source }}

This is TOUCH 1 of 6 — Day 1. Channel: EMAIL.
Angle: Warm follow-up. You reached out once and didn't hear back. Keep it short, reference the property specifically, ask if they have any questions. No pressure. Sign off with your name and phone: {{ $('Prep Fields').first().json.agent_phone }}

Write a subject line and email body. Format exactly as:
SUBJECT: [subject here]
BODY: [email body here]

Keep the body under 80 words. Warm and personal.

parameters.jsCode:
const text = $input.first().json.content[0].text.trim();
const subjectMatch = text.split('SUBJECT:')[1];
const bodyMatch = text.split('BODY:')[1];
const subject = subjectMatch ? subjectMatch.split('BODY:')[0].trim() : 'Following up';
const body = bodyMatch ? bodyMatch.trim() : text;
const p = $('Prep Fields').first().json;
return [{ json: { subject, body, ...p } }];

const p = $input.first().json;
const mailtoLink = 'mailto:' + p.email + '?subject=' + encodeURIComponent(p.subject) + '&body=' + encodeURIComponent(p.body);
const slackPayload = {
  blocks: [
    {
      type: 'header',
      text: { type: 'plain_text', text: '\u2709\ufe0f Touch 1 Email Ready \u2014 ' + p.lead_name, emoji: true }
    },
    {
      type: 'context',
      elements: [{ type: 'mrkdwn', text: 'Day 1 \u00b7 Cold nurture \u00b7 ' + p.property_address }]
    },
    {
      type: 'section',
      text: { type: 'mrkdwn', text: '*Subject:* ' + p.subject }
    },
    {
      type: 'section',
      text: { type: 'mrkdwn', text: '*Body:*\n>' + p.body.replace(/\n/g, '\n>') }
    },
    {
      type: 'section',
      text: { type: 'mrkdwn', text: '\u2709\ufe0f *<' + mailtoLink + '|Tap to send from your email>*' }
    }
  ]
};
return [{ json: { ...p, mailtoLink, slackPayload } }];

